<div id="review_508733" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/508733" />
    <a title="Eric G." class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/42476-eric-g"><img alt="Eric G." src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1376708348p2/42476.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/508733?book_show_action=true">Mar 31, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Eric G." class="user" itemprop="url" name="Eric G." href="/user/show/42476-eric-g">Eric G.</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42476-eric-g?shelf=philosophy">philosophy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42476-eric-g?shelf=politics">politics</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer508733" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16225695725432528079">Reform or Revolution is Rosa Luxemburg&apos;s stark response to Eduard Bernstein&apos;s book Evolutionary Socialism. Despite the fact that this book does hold small excerpts of brilliance that encompass Luxemburg&apos;s ability to combine passion with intelligence, her rebuttal was all but out of reach for me. That is, for a person with an elementary understanding of the political/social atmosphere of Germany between the dates 1880-1900. The Introduction by Mary-Alice Waters is satisfactory as it gives the con</span>
  <span id="freeText16225695725432528079" style="display:none">Reform or Revolution is Rosa Luxemburg's stark response to Eduard Bernstein's book Evolutionary Socialism. Despite the fact that this book does hold small excerpts of brilliance that encompass Luxemburg's ability to combine passion with intelligence, her rebuttal was all but out of reach for me. That is, for a person with an elementary understanding of the political/social atmosphere of Germany between the dates 1880-1900. The Introduction by Mary-Alice Waters is satisfactory as it gives the context and limited historical necessities. However, without having read Bernstein's work, I found myself lost within small sections that I could grasp (that detailed the economic theory of Marx etc.) and extended sections that directly countered the text I had not read. With an understanding that Luxemburg played a significant role in the evolution of socialist thinking, the text is an ample summary of her arguments and also, a concise insight into the plaguing factors of the Social Democratic parties of turn of the century Germany. </span>
  <a data-text-id="16225695725432528079" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review508733">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
        <a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link508733" title="Flag this review as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=508733&amp;resource_type=Review&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F213519.Reform_or_Revolution">flag</a>





      <span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_508733'><a id="like_count_review_508733" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/508733?resource_type=Review"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F213519.Reform_or_Revolution">Like</a></span>
